{
  "stem": "1873.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 312.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I will tell you something which sounds unbelievable, but is forever [INAUDIBLE] to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We was-- we were a few people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Ukrainian did behave wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was so good when food would come, he did give half to me and to my friend Wolf.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And night time, we did put four straw mattresses, straw sacks-- it's not like a mattress in America-- and we slept on it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because [INAUDIBLE] was the order to go asleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody could fall asleep anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the rule was that each one of us must tell the story of his life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So every day was something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember we had a guard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a-- a-- fellow, he was a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was able to imitate different instruments, fiddle, or trumpet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember we had a guard who did give us extra soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He promised us extra soup if, the next day, if he will-- he will imitate a fiddle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, so one night we had this and another night something else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when my turn had come to tell my story, it was short of a thing, [INAUDIBLE] and I'm here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when the turn was to Alvin Lippman, Alvin Lippman's story, something strange did come out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His story-- he told us a story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was [INAUDIBLE] in the army in Germany when Hitler conducted his [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His little revolt when he was arrested later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And General [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ludendorff ?] was leading a platoon of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he did march with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he as a young [INAUDIBLE], Alvin Lippman, was ordered to go with the-- with the soldiers by Ludendorff.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later, when the [NON-ENGLISH] failed, of course, some were wounded.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
